    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the Morrison COU1 CFD hemolysis model is accepted. Seven of thirteen factors were assessed and found to meet or exceed requirements. The remaining six factors were determined to be not required at Model Risk Level 2 for a Class II device under the applicable project risk framework. The model demonstrates sufficient credibility for its intended use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions, and the relative hemolysis index criterion RH < 1 is satisfied across all evaluated operating points.",
